Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 真寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞的是他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以哈罗 陪陪他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪在洛克昂·史特拉特斯的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪陪他吧 哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 明白
