Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离战斗宙域…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.09,0:10:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方部队总数为？
