Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给Alvatore就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
