Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:23.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気を見せつけても　強がっても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:28.21,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一人では生きられない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:32.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あの日の約束なら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:37.68,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の深くに残っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:42.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}As life goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:48.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れちゃいけないから Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:53.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't let it go...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.80,0:22:00.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この広い大地と仲間達のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:55.09,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}经久不变的笑颜　是这样的我们　在年轮中周而复始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:21:03.83,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}擦身而过的风景　却无法剪下收藏　唯心房中丝缕焦急
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:11.09,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}将无谓的自尊远远抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:16.73,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}用温柔将这个世界抱紧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:18.13,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I Gotta Say
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:23.41,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使告诉我你的勇气　即使逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:28.21,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一个人便无法生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:32.56,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那一日的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:37.68,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}于我心深处　只步未移
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:42.59,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}As life goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:48.38,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因为不能忘记 Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:53.19,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't let it go...
